name: 伊波尼
introduction: Ebony is an all American mixed breed rescue dog from Albuquerque, New Mexico. She is primarily a family pet who lives along with another dog and two cats that was primarily trained by one of her owners, Ms. Frances Cabeen. Ebony is active in canine agility and free style dancing winning multiple awards and grand champions. Ebony has worked in multiple commercials and performed at charity events, pet adoption drives, and homes for the elderly and sick children.
